{
  "text": "Thank you. We would like to thank Ra at this time for the opportunity to be of service of those in this sphere who would like to have the information that we gain here from assembly. You stated that pretty well one point it in service to others with the potential for alerting a great mass of white strength. I assume that the same holds precisely true for the service to self-clarity. Is this correct? I am well. This is incorrect, but subtly so invocation and evocation of what may be termed negative entities or qualities the expression alerts the positively oriented equivalent, however, those upon the service to others have wait to be called and can only send love.",
